Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.58,0:03:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,就是说 大家一起去温泉旅行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.72,0:03:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,大家一起去温泉旅行？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.87,0:03:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,温泉…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.86,0:03:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 那可是魅惑的清泉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.45,0:03:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,沐浴在温暖与自然之中 让暖流浸透
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.89,0:03:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那经日劳顿为工作与战斗所累的身心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.21,0:03:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,只要泡上一次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.47,0:03:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,就能万病回春
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.75,0:03:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,活血化瘀 舒筋活络
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.69,0:03:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 好舒服好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.13,0:03:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,泡进远离尘世喧嚣的温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.07,0:04:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,最能治愈你的身心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.50,0:04:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,景色也不错 看上去挺舒服的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.82,0:04:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,真想去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.37,0:04:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我已经决定要睡觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.58,0:04:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,所以不会去的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.98,0:04:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.21,0:04:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样说死了真的好么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.59,0:04:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.45,0:04:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,西部荒野的梦幻的神泉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.29,0:04:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,可是有返老还童的功效呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.27,0:04:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,明明只要泡一泡这温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.84,0:04:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,就能年轻十岁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.78,0:04:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,就能变回当年那个自己
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.93,0:04:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,当年那个肤若凝脂的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.89,0:04:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,年轻 真好 年轻 真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.02,0:04:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,各位 明天一早在气球起降场集合
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.50,0:04:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,罗吉 去让亚文在今天内把气球整备好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.20,0:04:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,琳卡也是 马上开始打点行装
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.59,0:04:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,给我等着 梦幻的神泉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.22,0:04:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我要泡上一整个假期
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.26,0:04:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,出发了 各位
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.13,0:04:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,噢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.32,0:05:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,再喊一次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.68,0:05:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,噢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.70,0:05:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 这样大家就都去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.79,0:05:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,好久没有和玛丽恩她们一起出门旅行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.96,0:05:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,好开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.14,0:05:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,睡衣和毛巾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.17,0:05:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,点心和牙刷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.15,0:05:16.59,Default,,0,258,121,,{\fs40}フラム
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.15,0:05:16.59,Default,,0,258,0,,{\fs27}火系炸弹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.15,0:05:16.59,Default,,200,0,121,,{\fs40.5}クラフト
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.15,0:05:16.59,Default,,200,0,0,,{\fs27}物理系炸弹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.15,0:05:16.59,Default,,0,0,56,,手雷和爆裂弹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.83,0:05:18.28,Default,,0,138,121,,{\fs40.5}レヘルン
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.83,0:05:18.28,Default,,0,138,0,,{\fs27}冰系炸弹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.83,0:05:18.28,Default,,0,0,56,,冰球和…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.28,0:05:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,喂为什么要这些啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.81,0:05:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,然后 还需要这个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.87,0:05:23.21,Default,,0,138,121,,{\fs40.5}オメガクラフト
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.87,0:05:23.21,Default,,0,138,0,,{\fs27}强化物理系炸弹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.87,0:05:23.21,Default,,0,0,56,,终极爆裂弹！？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.35,0:05:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,连这么强力的东西都要带啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.40,0:05:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,以防万一以防万一啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.43,0:05:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你好多行李啊 爱丝卡前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.30,0:05:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你都带了些什么啊 这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.79,0:05:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,因为薇尔贝尔她…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.47,0:05:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,薇尔贝尔？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.75,0:05:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 大家都到齐了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.86,0:05:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,看上去好像很沉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.89,0:05:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.92,0:06:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 未踏遗迹竟然离我们这么近了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.86,0:06:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.66,0:06:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好大呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.52,0:06:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,说起来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.66,0:06:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,听说柯尔赛特支部
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.92,0:06:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,是为了前往那座遗迹而设立的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.83,0:06:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然还没人能去到那里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.03,0:06:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我会去的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.64,0:06:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,总有一天 一定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.25,0:06:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,各位 看得到山了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.34,0:06:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,好大呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.54,0:06:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,在冒烟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.23,0:06:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.02,0:06:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是火山啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.30,0:06:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我还是第一次见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.09,0:06:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,能感觉到力量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.94,0:06:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的目的地就在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.26,0:06:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,终于快到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.58,0:06:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,返老还童的神泉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.64,0:06:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.50,0:06:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,好多蒸汽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.81,0:06:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,好热啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.11,0:06:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.67,0:06:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,神泉在哪里呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.23,0:06:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,不在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.93,0:06:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,在更深处
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.14,0:07:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,神泉就在那座火山的山脚下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.01,0:07:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,各位 向着山脚进发！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.42,0:07:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,好…好沉…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.27,0:07:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,温泉还没到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.70,0:07:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那边那个不是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.18,0:07:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.37,0:07:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,那不过就是一般的温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.29,0:07:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,一般的温泉？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.10,0:07:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,已经浑身是汗了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.05,0:07:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,薇尔贝尔 好想赶紧泡温泉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.90,0:07:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,随便哪儿都行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.76,0:07:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,还有一点点了 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.70,0:07:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是呀 爱丝卡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.95,0:07:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,可不能因为你还年轻就放弃哟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.80,0:07:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.32,0:07:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,爱丝卡 我帮你提包
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.28,0:07:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,谢…谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.96,0:07:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 离火山这么近了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.97,0:07:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.84,0:07:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,好强的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.26,0:07:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,玛丽恩 找到温泉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.20,0:08:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.97,0:08:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.67,0:08:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,力量更强大了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.05,0:08:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是这儿没错了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.89,0:08:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,终于到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.23,0:08:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,返老还童的神泉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.02,0:08:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,总算到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.13,0:08:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,但是还不能泡进去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.98,0:08:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,还有东西要调查一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.86,0:08:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,才不干 我可再等不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.94,0:08:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,这一行千辛万苦又平添了几道皱纹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.17,0:08:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,现在就要捞回来！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.02,0:08:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,班长 您先请
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.93,0:08:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我们先去那边搭帐篷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.94,0:08:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,多谢了 二位
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.67,0:08:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 先给我等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.93,0:08:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.20,0:08:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,来 来泡温泉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.55,0:08:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,薇尔贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.12,0:08:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.10,0:08:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,来 来 来 来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.58,0:08:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,呜哇 好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.14,0:08:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,好暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.95,0:08:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好滋润啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.49,0:09:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,疲惫的身体得以放松了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.62,0:09:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒的温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.25,0:09:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,都说了等等了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.71,0:09:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,算了 也好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.76,0:09:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服 顺便游个泳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.15,0:09:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,这样就一岁了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.90,0:09:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,这样就两岁了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.97,0:09:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这样就三岁了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.32,0:09:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你就这么想返老还童啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.46,0:09:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.42,0:09:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.37,0:09:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,有件事想请教一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.30,0:09:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,什么事啊 露希尔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.88,0:09:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,要怎么做才能长得大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.21,0:09:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.81,0:09:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,长得大？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.44,0:09:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,小后辈你还真有眼光呢 找爱丝卡问
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.99,0:09:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想问问爱丝卡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.58,0:09:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,要怎么做才能长得大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.15,0:09:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,喂喂 怎么妮欧你也…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.29,0:09:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这还不简单
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.73,0:09:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.69,0:09:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好好吃饭好好运动就行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.97,0:09:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.74,0:09:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,请你们看看我一直做的运动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.49,0:09:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,首先 脑子里想着胸肌…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.26,0:09:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,哈！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.37,0:10:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,呜哇 好麻烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.58,0:10:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,要这么费劲 还不如用魔法梆的一下变大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.45,0:10:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,梆的一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.06,0:10:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,然后让我揉一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.26,0:10:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你手在往哪伸啊妮欧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.05,0:10:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 没忍住
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.57,0:10:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 大家到底在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.21,0:10:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你问说什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.39,0:10:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,哇——
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.40,0:10:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,难道不是？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.33,0:10:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.11,0:10:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我是问身高了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.43,0:10:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,欸…欸…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.34,0:10:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,欸！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.26,0:10:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,欸！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.37,0:10:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,身高！？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.84,0:10:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是哪个最先误会的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.86,0:10:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不是爱丝卡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.02,0:10:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,是爱丝卡啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.06,0:10:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.83,0:10:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,爱丝卡前辈真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.99,0:10:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不是啦 露希尔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.41,0:10:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这不过是语言的多样性…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.66,0:10:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 不好意思啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.07,0:10:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 原来不是在说肌肉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.78,0:10:59.99,Title,,0,0,0,,{\an1\move(189,408,21,408)\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\fad(200,0)\blur7.5\bord3\t(0,920,2,\blur0\bord0\1c&HFBDEF8&)}玛丽恩·奎因
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.50,0:11:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿咻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.95,0:11:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思 亚文
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.40,0:11:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,让你陪我们开发班出来旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.04,0:11:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.68,0:11:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,其实我的梦想就是用自己的气球飞向世界的尽头
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.36,0:11:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,所以就当是在预演了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.75,0:11:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,世界的尽头…就是那个古老传说里的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.05,0:11:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你还有这样的梦想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.05,0:11:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不只是个普通的气球机务哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.52,0:11:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 那个气球到不了那么远的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.76,0:11:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,比如耗油量问题
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.02,0:11:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,还有长距离航行需要的强度什么的也不够吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.46,0:11:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,欸 你蛮懂的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.52,0:11:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,罗吉你也是憧憬蓝天的一员吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.52,0:11:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不 倒不是这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.16,0:11:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,这点想法 无论是谁都曾在脑海里闪现过的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.98,0:11:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,或许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.21,0:11:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我是觉得不熟悉气球的话是不知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.74,0:11:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我倒也说不上熟悉了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.78,0:11:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 要是感兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.74,0:11:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,随时欢迎来维修班哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.60,0:11:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,罗吉我们可是热烈欢迎的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.19,0:12:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.28,0:12:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,呐 不觉得从刚才开始变热了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.14,0:12:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这么说起来 好像确实温度升高了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.10,0:12:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.41,0:12:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 好像气泡…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.08,0:12:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,果然出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.20,0:12:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,欸 什么东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.43,0:12:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.37,0:12:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.87,0:12:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.56,0:12:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.82,0:12:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,欸！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.32,0:12:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,是哪个吃了熊心豹子胆的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.35,0:12:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,胆敢擅闯奴家的圣地！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.61,0:12:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,哇——！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.40,0:12:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.17,0:12:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.23,0:12:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,从温泉里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.64,0:12:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.98,0:12:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,浑身通红的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.75,0:12:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,妖怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.82,0:12:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那家伙是什么东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.76,0:12:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,火之王
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.34,0:12:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,火之王？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.78,0:12:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,司火 力量最为强大的精灵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.03,0:12:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直等着这一刻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.87,0:12:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,火之王！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.58,0:13:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,与我缔结契约吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.91,0:13:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,契约？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.64,0:13:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,契约是什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.21,0:13:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,薇尔贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.58,0:13:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,从前也跟姐姐一起去过…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.10,0:13:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那个时候是风之王就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.49,0:13:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.68,0:13:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你是魔法师啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.22,0:13:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,因为有点事由
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.56,0:13:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,想单刀直入跟你缔结契约
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.19,0:13:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,少废话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.60,0:13:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,就算你是魔法师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.77,0:13:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,奴家可不听人类使唤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.42,0:13:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,哇——！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.20,0:13:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,果然情绪一如传闻差得很呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.56,0:13:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,果然只能一战了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.94,0:13:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,爱丝卡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.80,0:13:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,轮到那些炸弹出场了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.60,0:13:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.45,0:13:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,给我等等 薇尔贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.02,0:13:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,难道你的目的其实是跟这个精灵碰面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.24,0:13:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.04,0:13:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.35,0:13:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMS PGothic\b0\bord1.5\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H7D4A2D&}(∀｀*ゞ)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.24,0:13:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMS PGothic\b0\bord1.5\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H7D4A2D&}(∀｀*ゞ) {\r}你个头啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.87,0:14:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 大婆婆突然联系我了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.50,0:14:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,薇尔贝尔 最近没向我报告修行的进展啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.40,0:14:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.14,0:14:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了——
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.52,0:14:10.49,Default,,0,0,88,,{\fs52.5}薇尔贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.22,0:14:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,修行早就忘到九霄云外去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.23,0:14:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,什么都没做啊怎么办呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.77,0:14:12.96,Default,,0,0,88,,{\fs52.5}薇尔贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.52,0:14:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.25,0:14:15.38,Default,,0,0,88,,{\fs52.5}薇尔贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.54,0:14:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,确实听说过火之王在这一带以西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.56,0:14:17.64,Default,,0,0,88,,{\fs52.5}薇尔贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.23,0:14:20.67,Default,,0,0,88,,{\fs52.5}薇尔贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.20,0:14:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,就像风之王那时候那样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.61,0:14:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,干净利落地签个契约就好了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.94,0:14:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,对哦 就这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.60,0:14:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,一个人多少有点不放心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.96,0:14:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,就把大家都叫上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.36,0:14:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,好过分！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.67,0:14:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,薇尔贝尔 你就这么瞒着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.98,0:14:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,还让爱丝卡带那么多炸弹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.54,0:14:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么不好嘛 帮我个忙而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.28,0:14:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你们那么强…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.80,0:14:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,好个头啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.58,0:14:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,少废话 少废话 少废话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.56,0:14:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,如今该奴家生气
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.76,0:14:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,奴家最讨厌人类了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.36,0:14:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,等… 请等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.02,0:14:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么讨厌人类啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.77,0:14:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,擅闯温泉这件事 我们道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.99,0:15:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.71,0:15:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,都从奴家的祭坛上抢去火焰了还有什么好说的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.52,0:15:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,从祭坛？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.79,0:15:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,抢去火焰？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.15,0:15:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是火之王说的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.39,0:15:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,被抢去火焰的祭坛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.28,0:15:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,破败不堪都已经在崩塌了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.79,0:15:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,或许是盗掘遗迹的家伙干的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.82,0:15:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这个洞是？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.27,0:15:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,这里曾经祭祀着精灵的宝玉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.32,0:15:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,精灵的宝玉？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.26,0:15:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才火之王说的那个被抢去的火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.92,0:15:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,大概就是曾经人类为火之王而打造
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.44,0:15:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,祭祀在此的宝玉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.27,0:15:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,听大婆婆说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.03,0:15:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,过去有着这样的习俗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.42,0:15:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是说 人类给火之王的供品
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.84,0:15:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,又被人类夺去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.77,0:15:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,难怪她会讨厌人类
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.07,0:15:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我来打造宝玉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.72,0:15:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.38,0:16:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我想救赎火之王
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.92,0:16:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,被曾经信赖的人类所背叛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.59,0:16:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,受了伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.30,0:16:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,所以才会那么生气
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.07,0:16:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,爱丝卡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.88,0:16:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,爱丝卡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.82,0:16:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 宝玉的做法咱们不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.94,0:16:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,打算怎么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.65,0:16:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我教你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.86,0:16:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,配方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.13,0:16:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,薇尔贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.60,0:16:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然超难超难超级难的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.36,0:16:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,就连老娘这样的大魔法师也做不了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.96,0:16:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 爱丝卡的话肯定能行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.32,0:16:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题吧 爱丝卡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.66,0:16:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,放心等着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.38,0:16:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就来做我们力所能及的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.62,0:16:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.89,0:16:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,琳卡和薇尔贝尔一起把石头重新整理好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.40,0:16:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我 妮欧和露希尔来清扫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.00,0:16:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.37,0:16:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就直接去采集素材了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.87,0:17:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,爱丝卡请把其他材料准备好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.66,0:17:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.45,0:17:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,首先是紫魂的水晶球
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.36,0:17:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.82,0:17:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,小心谨慎的话一定没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.44,0:17:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,爱丝卡 我们带回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.58,0:17:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,多谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.50,0:17:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.44,0:17:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这样就备齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.27,0:17:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来就拜托了 爱丝卡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.68,0:17:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,耐心等着我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.70,0:17:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,火之王
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.36,0:17:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对会救你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.89,0:17:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉我们来迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.09,0:17:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.05,0:17:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,大家去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.06,0:17:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,难道都被火之王烧化了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.28,0:17:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.02,0:18:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,看这招！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.27,0:18:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,这声音…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.23,0:18:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,薇尔贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.40,0:18:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.31,0:18:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多该进入终章了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.53,0:18:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,请看这晴空飞舞的火树银花
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.54,0:18:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,喔 真是漂亮的火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.65,0:18:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,挺有能耐的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.76,0:18:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不愧是薇尔贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.45,0:18:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.19,0:18:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.23,0:18:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,喔——
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.93,0:18:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么觉得大家都很开心…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.16,0:18:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,火之王的心情也不错的样子…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.67,0:18:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.61,0:18:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,哟 你们三个 好可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.37,0:18:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,咱薇尔贝尔大人的魔法秀已经演完了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.70,0:18:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.61,0:18:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我好想看的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.90,0:18:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.92,0:18:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,果不其然 不愧是爱丝卡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.93,0:19:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你能行…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.10,0:19:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,欸 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.15,0:19:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,地震？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.59,0:19:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,各位 危险！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.35,0:19:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这是怎么了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.00,0:19:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.57,0:19:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,奴家的圣域重新涌出火的力量了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.88,0:19:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒 奴家的烈火熊熊燃烧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.96,0:19:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这里 原来是如此烈火燎原
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.91,0:19:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,因为失却了那个宝玉 而失去了力量呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.63,0:19:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,好强大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.84,0:19:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不愧是火之王的圣域
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.60,0:20:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,值得嘉奖 炼金术士小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.40,0:20:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,看来你们和过往的人类不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.90,0:20:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,要是有什么困扰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.22,0:20:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,随时欢迎你们来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.22,0:20:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.10,0:20:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.19,0:20:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,至此这件事就落下帷幕了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.47,0:20:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.88,0:20:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,忘了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.96,0:20:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.62,0:20:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你来这里的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.38,0:20:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,喏 说出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.02,0:20:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,玛丽恩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.70,0:20:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.63,0:20:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,火之王
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.90,0:20:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,与我缔结契约那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.36,0:20:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不缔约也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.07,0:20:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.65,0:20:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.22,0:20:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我要变得更强
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.74,0:20:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,下次一个人来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.85,0:20:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,所以请等着我 直到那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.32,0:20:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,薇尔贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.16,0:20:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.07,0:20:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,约好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.37,0:21:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,期待着卿与奴家刀刃相向的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.69,0:21:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.36,0:21:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,好烫！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.74,0:21:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 总算能放松地泡温泉了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.74,0:21:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,修祭坛修得皮肤都干巴巴的了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.56,0:21:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,马上就要捞回来！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.81,0:21:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 好像有人…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.62,0:21:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,呀——！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.35,0:21:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.83,0:21:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么哥哥你们也在泡啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.83,0:21:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,可是我们还没泡上啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.49,0:21:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,回去之前也想稍微泡一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.24,0:21:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 先说一声嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.99,0:21:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,罗吉你这大笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.93,0:21:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么就砸我一个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.48,0:23:34.14,Default,,0,0,12,,砰！梦想破灭了！
